{"tid":1715283,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"我就快連新年假都被老細扣埋","createTime":"2019-11-13T05:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T05:25:11.000Z","uid":112207,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9601e3c702e2b23719e0225b28efd3b016146bb9","tid":1715283,"uid":112207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小妹係sogo某一間港資深藍美容產品店做sale屎既<br />\n大家都知近排sogo咩事啦<br />\n咁佢開唔到門既時候 佢就突然send個msg比同事話 今日唔洗番變扣假<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鋪頭仲要完全唔比人坐<br />\n我膝頭痛到想出去游行都頂唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左生計 一日半日我可以忍<br />\n但今個月 佢已經係咁扣我例假扣到我下個月例假都冇晒 可能要連踩10日以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上成間公司d高層都藍到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小妹已經決定左要辭工<br />\n但我聖誕既紅日都被公司放晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我現在辭職 我驚要賠錢<br />\n想請問大家有冇勞工法例可以保障員工既假期唔可以比人咁迫放 同埋一個月通知期 如果我仲差佢假 我洗唔洗賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02288a31501a847df5ffdf02d27c5f5e136727a2","tid":1715283,"uid":215901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:09:43.000Z","msg":"再推<br />\n<br />\n醒目d啦連登仔<br />\n<br />\n你地唔撚理我再開 我屋企好多曱甴 幫拖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712452</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b5fedf43a2cd19e1bbb724fd15d5d6cf036e3080","tid":1715283,"uid":272914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"邊間？開名啦咁仆街間公司"},{"pid":"598cc168b779222a078cb63a418f903047311fe5","tid":1715283,"uid":90305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:19:33.000Z","msg":"你有冇即時agree? 係如口頭同message同意。如有就冇得講。<br />\n<br />\n 按《僱傭條例》，年假的日期應由僱主在徵詢僱員或其代表後指定。僱主須至少在假期開始的14天前以書面通知僱員年假的日期；如雙方同意，可以較短時間通知。換句話說，只要給予足夠的通知期，僱主仍然有決定員工放假日的可能。<br />\n<br />\n如果冇agreement, 要14日前通知。你可以打上勞工處問的。"},{"pid":"5999a351930c2cfab9e209600ac1971a63f3bb66","tid":1715283,"uid":200957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:20:20.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},{"pid":"d432ccd9d8ee1f62fc92b85f661d205f511a4829","tid":1715283,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:23:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">遊</span>行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 開名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ea39df110d42dac76c205f237b73bac27dfa0b","tid":1715283,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:25:11.000Z","msg":"請大家幫幫手做緊「公司處理三罷手法既問卷」，做完麻煩傳出去，想記錄低不同公司做法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/8c3ttZYfqRdd3ssNA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F8c3ttZYfqRdd3ssNA&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaYc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=96f7ed62\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/8c3ttZYfqRdd3ssNA</a>"}]}